This reverts commit fb153b07a90580df1a0c41bbe6ae143c9f8027d3.
Merge branch 'dev'

Update queue refill logic

- Contains a new check to ensure that the current RSS feed has a new
batch of articles before adding that batch to the queue.
Merge branch 'dev' to deploy new bot that posts once per hour
Forgot to comment out the testing statements and added submission to reddit

Changed bot so that it only posts articles once per hour
	-added a queue file stored in JSON format
	-the bot reads from the feed and adds things to the queue that
		a. haven't been posted
		b. aren't already in the queue
	-the bot posts the top item in the queue and removes it
	-it then rewrites the queue to the JSON file
Update README.md
